  "description": [
    "T EVENING NEWS 5 Cent a Copy MIDDIESBOWJUGH KY TUESDAY MAY 3 111915 25 Cents a Week Five Thousand Troops to Be Sent To the Phillipines Over Which the Stars and Stripes Now Floats CUBA IS GETTING TOO WARM IN SPOTS FOR THE SPANISH ADMIRAL OU GLORY WAVES TO s OVER PHILLIPINES UP COMMODORE Special to Evening News Washington May 3 Commodore George Washington Dewey commanding the Asiatic squadfon is to be made an Admiral GET ALL YOU CAN HOLD ALL YOU GET Special to Evening News Washington May 3 330 p m Cab inet has decided to send five thousand troops to hold the Phillipines A VERY NATURAL DIFFICULTY Special to Evening News Cadiz Spain Second Spanish squadron almost ready for service Difficulty in getting men and money Special to Evening News New York May 3 145 p m Wail street agency says that Manila has fallen and that the Stars and Stripes now wave over the Phillipines s DEPARTMENTS MAY GET FOOLED Special to Evening News Washington May 3 Departments believe Spain cant last much longer BOMBARDMENT BEGUN THEN CABLE CUT Special to Evening News London No cable from Manila since ten oclock yesterday London time Latest showed"
